COMMERCIAL LICENSING

This repository contains the open-source engineering kernel of the Causal Time
Protocol (CTP/IP). The canonical physics, Guardian Gates, and Git hook enforcement
are freely available for inspection, research, education, and non-commercial use.

Commercial deployment of CTP/IP — including but not limited to operating the LUX
Runtime, integrating the seal pipeline into products or services, issuing ZK-TSL
certificates, collecting fees via the CVF engine, or offering DGENCY certification
— requires a commercial license from Design Ledger PTY LTD.

